				<div style="font-style:italic">- Amplifying abilities are now capped at 10 times original strength.<br />
- Amplifying abilities no longer works for all abilities in the ability line. Diminishing returns still applies to everything in the ability line.<br />
- If an ability is taken to full amplification strength it will now experience an extended refresh time.</div>
			
		</td>
