		<div id="post_message_1139428">
                  
                  I completely understand, that game is more PVE focused, but the some sorcs problems on PVP servers, force us to reroll class. <br />
 As an example, with sorc i avoid Khal and other populated areas and forced to use bank where in a deaf place, for the reason, that us is simple one-two-shooting while browsing broker/bank or reading mail. <br />
<br />
 Use of protection against one type of magic can't help because <br />
<i>1) There's no time to define who and with what type of magic actually attacked you<br />
2) There is no protection from melee (Force barrier/7% mitigation - don't help when you getting hitted for 1.5-2k+</i>, Any melee fighter which is close (there is always someone close in city), simply 2-shooting sorc, and there no time to turn and use C.Spray/Sleep, because sorc is already dead<br />
<br />
From my point of view, looking at other classes as druid, bloodmage, it would be logical: <b> <br />
1) Join all 6 &quot; xxxx Sanctuary &quot; into 1 (Anti magic shield). <br />
2) To add similar protection from melee damage. </b> <br />
<br />
PS. Sorcs class lead can try on Tharridon, in bank, as on 40 + levels, feel sorcs... Or after recalling. <br />
And we cannot run away from bind/bank/mailbox  while druids/bloodmages/etc have time to consider situation (2 hits absorb + recast, or 9 sec invul + invul from some types of magic)<br />
<br />
Excuse my poor english
                  
