While i just reduced to dust 49/50 5D.<br />
Melee dont have such a HUGE dmg reduction.<br />
<br />
Get a Rogue47, have him dps a 47 4D, then have him DPS a 52 5D<br />
Do the same thing with a Sor47.<br />
<br />
The sorcerer will probably do 2 3 times more dmg vs the 47.<br />
